column4: <content>2 views of Naples by [Charles-Leopold] Grevenbroeck, on copper, signed and dated 1757, seen May 1974 at John Faustus, Antiquarian Books, 94 Jermyn Street. On gives a round view of the harbour comparable to Bruegel, though taken from a different point.</content>
